    public class Environment
extends PredicateReader
implements SisyphusPredicates
    This is class extends PredicateReader just as required to in the assignment. You can extend this class to include your predicate definitions or you can create another class that extends PredicateReader and use that one.

    I have defined this class as a singleton.
